text: Ika Yuliana Rochmawati is an Indonesian archer. She was born on 2 July 1989. Yuliana Rochmawati competed at the 2008 Summer Olympics, 2012 Summer Olympics, and the 2016 Summer Olympics.Ika RochmawatiIka Yuliana ROCHMAWATI == References == Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Indonesian archers Category:Olympians for Indonesia
